title: Wouter Corstjens
text: Wouter Corstjens (born 13 February 1987) is a Dutch-born Belgian <a href="association%20football">football</a> defender, who currently plays for <a href="K.%20Patro%20Eisden%20Maasmechelen">K. Patro Eisden Maasmechelen</a> on loan from <a href="K.V.C.%20Westerlo">Westerlo</a>.
